p.d: A new summer of love starts tonight as Caroline Flack welcomes 2019's line up of young singles to the villa. Iain Stirling also returns as show narrator with his inimitable take on all the island action. As the class of 2019 couple up and settle in, the battle to stay on the island - and win the ?50,000 prize begins. Get ready for a holiday romance to remember as the sun rises on Love Island.
